<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: right;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;"><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Charter<font size="4">ed By&nbsp;</font>The British Schools&nbsp;<font size="4">Founda<font size="4">t<font size="4">ion</font></font></font><br></i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear Parents,</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">I have had the privilege of spending two days last week at the school. As well as continuing my transition work, I also had a great opportunity to meet with parents and discuss future parental engagement strategies. I have been made to feel extremely welcome at the school and I am learning more and more about the school as time progresses. I would like to thank all the families I have met to date for your openness, honesty and desire to further improve and strengthen our crucial partnership.</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">I was pleased to outline my vision for parental engagement at BSY moving forward. I believe that there should be as many methods of communication to suit the differing needs of parents as is possible. I outlined a very detailed list of communication that the school might use including:</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">PTA or PTG with a very clear remit</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Focus groups for key developments</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Principal Q&amp;A sessions</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Coffee mornings</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">School App</font></li></ul></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The list was exhaustive and could easily be added to over time. However, we do need to be clear on what methods will be used effectively for parents to easily access information.</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">I also outlined my desire for parents to be involved more in recruitment of senior staff to the school, school accreditations, formulating and testing the school mission, reviewing our aims and supporting the school admissions process with new families.</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">I would envisage that by the end of the first school term we will have launched consultation on many of the key areas and finalised a coherent communications policy and strategy for the school. I have made it clear that I am keen to hear the views and opinions <b>of all</b> parents where possible through whatever means suits individual families.</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">I shall be visiting Yangon again in mid July before taking a short break in the UK to visit family. I will be back to Yangon at the end of July to continue the transition work to the new academic year. I am very excited about this new challenge for me and feel honoured to be able to play a significant role in the new start for the school at the new campus.</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">I shall be writing to you all again in August with a timeline for the development of our parent engagement strategies and opportunities for your input and feedback.</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">In the meantime, I would like to wish you all a very relaxing, safe and happy summer holiday, whatever your plans are.</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">I look forward to working with you all on a permanent basis once I have formally moved to Yangon.</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Kind regards,</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Paul Holyome</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">New Principal</font></div><span lang="en-GB" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: start;"><div style="margin: 0px;"><br></div></span><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style=""><i style=""><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600" style="" face="Arial, sans-serif"><b style="">World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font></div></div>]]></td>
